27:48.680 --> 27:50.000
dia ditimpa masalah.

27:52.270 --> 27:54.110
Di depan dia, saya selalu berpura-pura

27:54.110 --> 27:55.590
saya tak tahu apa-apa.

27:59.680 --> 28:00.550
